WEBVTT

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:01.976
and left them out
for the terrorists to burn.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:04.936
Today, the collection
lies hidden in Bamako,

00:01:04.959 --> 00:01:06.336
the capital of Mali,

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:08.456
moldering in the high humidity.

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:10.336
What was rescued by ruse

00:01:10.360 --> 00:01:12.096
is now once again in jeopardy,

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:13.360
this time by climate.

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:16.616
But Africa, and the far-flung
corners of the world,

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.936
are not the only places,
or even the main places

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:23.256
in which manuscripts that could change
the history of world culture

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:24.800
are in jeopardy.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:30.656
